OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSewage regularly dumped    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fillegally in England and   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FWales rivers               
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Untreated sewage is being dumped       
OL,6, illegally in rivers across the country 
OL,7, on a regular basis, analysis shown to  
OL,8, the BBC suggests.                      
OL,10,FIt found seven water companies in      
OL,11,FEngland and Wales discharged untreated 
OL,12,Fsewage into rivers and the sea more    
OL,13,Fthan 3,000 times between 2017 and 2021.
OL,15,FThe water industry admitted action was 
OL,16,Fneeded to address the problem.         
OL,18,FThe fresh data comes a week after MPs  
OL,19,Fwarned of a "chemical cocktail" of     
OL,20,Fpollutants tainting England's rivers.  
